Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到了  這是第二個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.25,0:01:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦打開這扇門就無法抽身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必口述了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水 宇水 你在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.33,0:02:08.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是 吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.51,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.91,0:02:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十九話 被心眼鎖住的狼\N爆裂牙突零式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.63,0:02:44.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼 不放馬過來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會把你們倆的人頭\N跟志志雄的人頭一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿來裝飾我的慶功宴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇水 你在亂說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的話\N若是傳入志志雄大人耳中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.31,0:02:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再宣告一次好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.02,0:03:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會的話\N我隨時會跟志志雄決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.26,0:03:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,志志雄知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.99,0:03:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然知道\N但他還是需要我這個心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.96,0:03:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打消念頭了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.07,0:03:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那把小刀連隻貓都殺不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.95,0:03:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安慈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來拔刀齊留下的藥效果不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.49,0:03:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在照顧我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.93,0:03:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不知道藥是誰調的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.30,0:03:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你是有很多好同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全身都是傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.97,0:04:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 這個痛楚太痛快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.24,0:04:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這感覺還是\N與劍心交手後首次感受到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.48,0:04:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去第二個對手  宇水那堣F
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.45,0:04:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他知道十本刀去葵屋急著趕路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十本刀跑去葵屋了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在去還趕得上拔刀齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 就在前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要對那讓我倆重逢的命運之神\N不 是佛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說聲謝謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.61,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟你下次還是可能會再交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 到時我會讓自己進步的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.35,0:04:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次一定用這拳頭打敗你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.67,0:05:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個子特別的小的  是拔刀齊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.64,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你那冷汗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.11,0:05:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道葵屋的危機啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.25,0:05:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 安慈那傢伙早就背叛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必囉唆了\N你快決定是否讓開那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.96,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左之助 你沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 下一個是這位嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.47,0:05:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來安慈那傢伙\N一個人也沒殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你若是不讓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要生氣是很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.18,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是別著急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.74,0:05:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那會製造多餘的緊張\N使實力減半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.18,0:05:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這傢伙給我應付你快趕路去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算葵屋的人被全部殺光\N也要留在這媥埶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是志志雄大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.40,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著 不准擅自…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.66,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了  你也來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 可以碰我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.07,0:06:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有志志雄大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.90,0:06:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很美麗的友情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.34,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你比傳聞中的更天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.88,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來你的心眼已經看徹底了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓那個一直該殺而未殺\N的拔刀齊留在這
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太礙事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會妨礙我殺你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等 你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別以為宇水會被殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他會打倒齊藤的\N然後下一個就輪到你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.97,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤不會被那傢伙殺死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.67,0:06:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道  宇水的心眼有多強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的心眼聞到血腥味\N會變得更敏銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼人  殺  殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.05,0:07:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,右邊第三個你的架式很不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.29,0:07:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是薩摩的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別怕 大家先退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.87,0:07:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 知道了  我一個人過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.37,0:07:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想讓自己人有更多犧牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.87,0:07:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先使人大意\N然後再從左右兩邊偷襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.04,0:07:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有夠卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.95,0:07:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實像現在的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.65,0:07:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驚訝變成恐懼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.95,0:07:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你內心的動向我可是瞭若指掌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.50,0:07:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太天真了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.64,0:07:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會讓你痛苦最久\N直到你心臟停止為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 大概還要數到三吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一、二、三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的絕招像神一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.96,0:08:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺？要殺死我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很激動哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.44,0:08:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.24,0:08:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怨恨我在神戶\N殺死了你五十個警察同伴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.01,0:08:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算眼睛失明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.24,0:08:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心眼還是把你摸清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.41,0:08:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,摸透你的心情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我的心眼之前\N沒有任何事是可以隱藏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.82,0:08:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報仇也是一種正義  很好很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.63,0:08:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心眼不是妖術魔術之流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.67,0:08:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你能讀出我的心理狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.94,0:08:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻讀不出我的思考
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.01,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保護日本的治安與民眾的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.11,0:09:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是警察的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.61,0:09:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如同過去的新撰組
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.61,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.62,0:09:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦站上那個職位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.28,0:09:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在任務過程中喪命\N是理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.65,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不像拔刀齊會在意很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.46,0:09:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒有任何報仇的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心眼若是看不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能讓我興奮的只有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.27,0:09:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惡、即、斬\N是為我的正義而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.71,0:09:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前新撰組第三隊組長 齊藤一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有你當對手\N我沒什麼不滿足的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你的熱血濺在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是傳聞評價極高的絕招\N「牙突」 嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.99,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.10,0:09:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寶劍寶玉百花繚亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有三個傷口   了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.28,0:10:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你表情似乎很不解哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道我是如何瞄準攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如何防止你的牙突的尖端的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想知道嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.32,0:10:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如你所說心眼不是妖術之流的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心眼的真面目是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幕末的某一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我與志志雄對峙  失去視力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.70,0:10:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去用處的我\N就那樣被幕府隨意拋棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.84,0:10:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡過地獄般的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連自己在哪都不曉得誤入山中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.31,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在生死關頭徘徊\N最後終於用盡力氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我分不出日夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也分不出自己是活的還是死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.56,0:11:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對 我的心臟\N確實有一瞬間是停止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是流水的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的喉嚨強烈乾渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.72,0:11:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跑啊 不斷地跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跑到那聲音的源頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後那時候我注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我居然聽到遠方小河的流動聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.77,0:11:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在死亡邊緣繞了一圈\N又復甦回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.97,0:11:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而有了異常聽覺的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.78,0:11:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有這能力以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類的聲音、心臟的鼓動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心理狀態、骨頭的磨擦聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,筋肉的伸縮聲、攻擊姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.32,0:12:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都會經由聲音告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我無敵的心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在心眼前面\N牙突跟普通的刺擊沒兩樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心跳稍微加快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.37,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的穿著很可笑\N原來你的腦袋也是一樣可笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你的高論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了答謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也讓你見識我的心眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心眼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的心眼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.10,0:12:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的心眼不是你那種異常聽覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的是超越生死線\N只有劍客才能體會的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.87,0:12:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡單一句話 就是洞察力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼你的心眼看到什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.51,0:13:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 你成為\N志志雄的同伴的真正理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死志志雄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.12,0:13:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你講歸講\N那並不是你真正所想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.16,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你發表高論\N提及被志志雄奪走光明時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.30,0:13:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那應該是你最痛恨的過去\N你竟然微笑談論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.67,0:13:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是我知道了 你放棄報仇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.51,0:13:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為自己得到心眼\N自己變強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.84,0:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是與你重逢的志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.45,0:13:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比穿越生死線\N變強後的你還要強
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算與他交手  你還是必輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.02,0:13:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸的話 過去你人生的努力\N就全歸於無了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是你設下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.13,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有機會就隨時能\N殺死志志雄的條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.83,0:13:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受加入十本刀的提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要你虛張聲勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.64,0:14:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說要殺死志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.28,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少周圍的人\N不會察覺到你的敗北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣 沒說中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也相差不遠了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.85,0:14:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.02,0:14:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,齊藤一  你的心眼確實了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是心眼的使用者\N有我一個就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.69,0:14:54.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要以我真正的絕招  打死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢戰鬥\N只會捲起尾巴吠叫的喪家犬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.20,0:15:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少叫得那麼大聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.34,0:15:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龜甲之盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你那堶  有什麼機關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之世上沒有我的牙突\N刺不穿的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機關？你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.06,0:15:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個盾牌只是利用龜甲的圓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來滑開敵人武器的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,同時封住敵人的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是用這個槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刺你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.02,0:15:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我的故鄉\N琉球的王家秘傳武術之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盾牌與槍的基本戰法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還想再用牙突嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.99,0:16:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新撰組的一貫傳統是\N把一個絕招昇華成絕對的絕招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.43,0:16:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到最後\N你除了牙突以外無計可施啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惜你使出牙突的瞬間\N就被我的心眼看穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上沒有招術能\N破解我這三連動作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝負分出了哦 齊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你死得痛快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.53,0:16:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你察覺到連志志雄\N都不知道的我的心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我要讓你後悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來你無法打倒志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.74,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就藉口殺死弱者來\N出那口嘔氣啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.21,0:16:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說志志雄沒察覺到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.68,0:16:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男人不可能這麼笨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.95,0:17:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕…他早看穿你的心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.89,0:17:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而假裝不知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.43,0:17:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你陳腐的自尊心\N被他巧妙的利用了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒注意到的人是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.81,0:17:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個怎樣 這距離你無法用牙突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.71,0:17:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,視線也被擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的你\N等於遮住眼睛的不倒翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不信你還能說大話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快吧 快害怕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.29,0:17:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一擊我會從盾牌後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刺擊你的臉 殺死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.06,0:17:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看不見我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我的心眼看穿了你所有行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 剛剛那個是牙突嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,牙突有幾種型式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通的是第一式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由斜上方往下刺擊是第二式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對空迎擊用的第三式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.98,0:18:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及…剛才那是最後一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.14,0:18:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在沒有間距的密著狀態下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用上半身的彈性\N使出的 「零式」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.28,0:18:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這都是為了與拔刀齊決鬥時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保留的絕招 你感到光榮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 若是志志雄還有話說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.93,0:18:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不該是這樣的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.30,0:18:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不戰而服志志雄時\N你就該拋棄劍道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種無法貫徹信念的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.34,0:19:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論死活都是很慘的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個男人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,講話真是毫不保留啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.12,0:19:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想要我安慰你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.39,0:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說 一點猶豫也沒有\N貫徹自己的信念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.49,0:19:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看似簡單 其實是最難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.40,0:19:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在今後近代化的明治中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.97,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能如何為劍而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.94,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貫徹你的惡、即、斬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.55,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會貫徹到死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.49,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緋村預料的事發生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.03,0:19:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於要展開決戰了\N大家都準備好了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.23,0:20:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒對方之前  先保護好自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.17,0:20:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然了\N我不會讓自己人死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.67,0:20:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人士兵大約150人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.87,0:20:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺不能戰鬥\N我們一個人得應付20人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.45,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 那邊的小弟\N你別搞錯了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.92,0:20:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙只是\N防止你們逃走的牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.09,0:20:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的對手是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.33,0:20:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了  快點死心快點出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.10,0:20:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要砍下你們的人頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.60,0:20:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當作給志志雄大人的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣志志雄大人一定…
